---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Old World Rankings"
  description="How Old World Rankings collects, uses, and protects your personal data."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="text-gray-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Old World Rankings ("OWR", "the Platform", "we", "us") is operated by <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Tributech Pty Ltd</strong> (ABN 65 140 774 876), an Australian company. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">2.1 Account Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            When you create an account — either directly or via third-party authentication (Google, Microsoft) — we collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Name and display name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Password (stored securely using industry-standard hashing) — or authentication token if using social login</li>
            <li>Region/country selection</li>
            <li>Profile photo (optional, or imported from your social login provider)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">2.2 Tournament and Gaming Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">When you use the Platform, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Tournament registrations, results, and placings</li>
            <li>Army list compositions</li>
            <li>Player rankings and performance statistics</li>
            <li>Gallery images and descriptions you upload</li>
            <li>Matchup and scoring data</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">2.3 Data from Third-Party Platforms</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We aggregate publicly available tournament results from various sources including third-party tournament platforms, spreadsheet uploads, and manual entry by tournament organisers. This data may include your name, placings, faction choices, and army list selections from events you have participated in — regardless of whether you have an OWR account.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">2.4 Payment Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            If you subscribe to OWR Pro or register for paid tournaments, payment is processed by Stripe. We do not store your credit card details. Stripe's privacy policy governs payment data.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">2.5 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect standard technical data including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Device type</li>
            <li>Pages visited and interaction patterns</li>
            <li>Referral source</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Provide and maintain the Platform — rankings, tournament management, army lists</li>
            <li>Display your tournament results and rankings publicly</li>
            <li>Process payments for subscriptions and tournament registrations</li>
            <li>Send transactional emails (account confirmation, tournament updates, password resets)</li>
            <li>Improve the Platform through analytics</li>
            <li>Enforce our Terms of Service and prevent abuse</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            We do not use your personal information for marketing or advertising purposes. We do not sell your data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Public Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            The following information is public by default and visible to all Platform users:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Display name</li>
            <li>Region</li>
            <li>Tournament results and placings</li>
            <li>Rankings and performance statistics</li>
            <li>Army lists submitted to tournaments</li>
            <li>Gallery images you upload</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            This is inherent to the competitive and community nature of the Platform. Tournament results and rankings are public information, similar to sports statistics.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Cookies and Analytics</h2>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">5.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We use a session cookie to keep you logged in. This is necessary for the Platform to function and does not require consent.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">5.2 Privacy-Focused Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We use Umami for privacy-focused analytics. Umami does not use cookies, does not collect personal information, and does not track users across sites. All data is aggregated and anonymous.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">5.3 Google Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            With your consent, we use Google Analytics to understand how the Platform is used. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymous usage data. You can decline analytics cookies via the consent banner, and Google Analytics will not load.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-3">5.4 Consent Cookie</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Your analytics cookie preference is stored in a cookie shared across the marketing site and the main application so you only need to choose once.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">We use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Authentication:</strong> Google and Microsoft for social login (OAuth)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Payment processing:</strong> Stripe for subscriptions and tournament payments</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Analytics:</strong> Umami (privacy-focused, cookieless) and Google Analytics (with consent)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Tournament data:</strong> Results aggregated from third-party tournament platforms, direct uploads (including spreadsheets), and manual entry by tournament organisers</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Each third-party service has its own privacy policy governing how it handles your data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">We share your information only in these circumstances:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Public display:</strong> Tournament results, rankings, and army lists are displayed publicly on the Platform (see Section 4)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Tournament organisers:</strong> When you register for a tournament, the TO can see your registration details</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Payment processing:</strong> Stripe processes payments on our behalf</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Authentication providers:</strong> Google/Microsoft receive only the data necessary for login</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Legal requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">8. User-Submitted Content</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Players and tournament organisers submit data to OWR including tournament results, army lists, event details, and gallery images. We do not control the accuracy or content of user submissions. We perform moderation on gallery entries but do not guarantee review of all submitted content.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            If you believe content on the Platform infringes your rights or is inaccurate, contact us and we will investigate.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">9. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We retain your data for as long as your account is active. Tournament results and rankings are retained indefinitely as part of the historical competitive record, even if your account is deleted — though your name can be anonymised on request.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Automatically collected analytics data is retained in aggregated form and cannot be traced to individual users.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">10. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Access</strong> your personal data by contacting us</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Correct</strong> inaccurate information via your account settings or by contacting us</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Delete</strong> your account and associated personal data (right to erasure)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Restrict</strong> processing of your data in certain circumstances</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Data portability</strong> — request a copy of your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Object</strong> to processing of your data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Opt out</strong> of analytics cookies via the consent banner</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Request anonymisation</strong> of your name in historical tournament records</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at the address below. We will respond within 30 days.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Note: Deleting your account does not remove publicly available tournament results that were aggregated from third-party platforms, as this data exists independently of your OWR account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">11. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encrypted connections (HTTPS), secure password hashing, and access controls. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">12. Children</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            OWR is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, contact us and we will delete it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">13. International Users</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            OWR is operated from Australia. If you access the Platform from outside Australia, your information may be transferred to and processed in Australia. By using the Platform, you consent to this transfer.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">14. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify registered users of material changes via email or an in-app notice. The "last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">15. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            For privacy-related inquiries, data access requests, or complaints, contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Tributech Pty Ltd</strong><br />
            ABN 65 140 774 876<br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:data@oldworldrankings.com" class="text-gray-900 dark:text-owr-gold underline underline-offset-4">data@oldworldrankings.com</a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            If you are not satisfied with our response, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the
            <a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-900 dark:text-owr-gold underline underline-offset-4">Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC)</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
